snippet.title: DUELISTS // Official Launch Cinematic Trailer - VALORANT
snippet.description:
The fight’s just getting started. Click here, play now: https://riot.com/3gBWPLo

VALORANT, the 5v5 character-based tactical shooter from Riot Games is free to download and play right now.
